<div class="container getstarted">
  	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Welcome! This guide will teach you how to use the app. First, to have an easy experience navigating to Hallit from your mobile device, tap <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span> to enter your home, then proceed to add Hallit to your homescreen. Kindly do this now! and return back here.</p>
