  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tapping on your browser <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left"></span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-right"></span> buttons will enable you go back and forth during a session on the app</p>
  <br /><br /><br /> 	

  <p class="getcent"><span class="getcentt glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></p>
  <p class="font-fam getstarth">Explore</p>	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tapping on your map-marker will allow you view halls from all over the world</p>
  <br /><br /><br />
    
