  <p class="font-fam getstarth">New hall</p>	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tapping on the camera will enable you create and share a new hall. <%= link_to "Learn how to make hall", howtomakeahall_path, class: "gtstlearnhall" %> </p>
  <br /><br /><br />

  <p class="getcent"><span class="getcentt glyphicon glyphicon-heart-empty"></p>
  <p class="font-fam getstarth">Activity</p>	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tap on the heart button to view activities of friends or channels you follow</p>
  <br /><br /><br />
  
  <p class="getcent"><span class="getcentt glyphicon glyphicon-search"></p>
  <p class="font-fam getstarth">Search</p>	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tap on the search button to find friends and also discover users</p>
  <br /><br /><br />
  
  <p class="getcent"><img src="/assets/images/av.PNG" class="imggtst"/></p>
  <p class="font-fam getstarth">Avatar</p>	
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tap on your avatar to find links like Profile, Settings, Invite, Guide and to signout</p>
  <br /><br />
  
  <p class="font-fam getstarth">Essential</p>
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tapping on photos will allow you to view them</p>  
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Tapping on usernames on any profile page will allow you quickly find information such as; number of halls, following and followers </p>
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">When you find friends or channels you love, tap on the follow button to follow</p>
  <p class="font-fam1 getstartp">Thank you for using our guide. If you require any additional information, reach us on twitter @hallitservice and we'll be sure to reply you.</p>

